title: Teenagers in the Universe (Otroki vo vselennoj)

sources.title: Teenagers in the Universe (Otroki vo vselennoj)
sources.description: The best Soviet fantastic film for children. Film continuation "From Moscow To Cassiopeia" (Moskva-Kassiopeya) Director: Richard Viktorov Cast: Misha Ershov, Sasha Grigoriev, Volodya Savin, Volodya Basov, Olya Bityukova, Nadya Ovcharova, Ira Popova, Dima Ledogorov, Innokenti Smoktunovsky, Lev Durov, Vasili Merkuriev, Nataliya Fateeva, Igor Ledogorov, Raisa Ryazanova. Maxim Gorky film studio USSR, 1974
